{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, it was necessary to generate sequences of spectra of the desired length using the following algorithm:",
    "Given: samples Sp 1 …Sp N, set of spectra for every sample, sequence length L, batch size B 1.",
    "Randomly choose a single sample Sp i from available samples. 2.",
    "Randomly sample (with replacement) L spectra from the set of Sp i spectra 3.",
    "Repeat steps 1 and 2 until B sequences are collected In this way, we inherently guarantee that the probability of being selected is the same for each sample, even though different numbers of spectra are available for different samples."
  ]
}